  <description>
    <p>Toggle between light and dark themes for a variety of different applications at the click of a button</p>
    <p>Yin and Yang allows you to uniformly change theme for a growing list of desktop applications on command.</p>
    <p>Main features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Toggle between light and dark mode</li>
      <li>Use Ctrl + Q or Escape to exit</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Current Yin-Yang Integrations</p>
    <ul>
      <li>GTK Theme</li>
      <li>Desktop "Prefer Dark"</li>
      <li>Visual Studio Code</li>
      <li>Terminal</li>
      <li>Code</li>
      <li>Firefox</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
